{\pard \ql \f0 \sa180 \li720 \fi0 VibeSwap proves that self-interest and collective benefit aren\u8217't opposed \u8212- they\u8217're aligned. Protocol fees go to contributors via Shapley distribution. Governance decays to zero. The protocol becomes a natural system, not a political one.\par}
